body!

14
00:01:35,517 --> 00:01:38,976
once told me the world is gonna roll me,

15
00:01:39,320 --> 00:01:42,628
I ain't the sharpest tool in the sheeed.

16
00:01:43,384 --> 00:01:45,396
She was lookin' kind of dumb

17
